look delicious.

00:00:24.315 --> 00:00:26.192 position:50% align:center line:84%
How yummy!

00:00:26.276 --> 00:00:29.571 position:50% align:center line:84%
[KANATA] Those are Haruka's
specialty. Omelet sandwiches.

00:00:29.654 --> 00:00:32.323 position:50% align:center line:84%
[AYUMU] A bunch of clubs
sent us really unique gifts.

00:00:32.407 --> 00:00:34.200 position:50% align:center line:84%
It's kind of overwhelming.

00:00:34.284 --> 00:00:36.077 position:50% align:center line:84%
