That's our school's middle name.

00:00:36.161 --> 00:00:39.247 position:50% align:center line:84%
Hey, girls. You gotta see this.

00:00:39.330 --> 00:00:40.582 position:50% align:center line:84%
[GROUP gasping]

00:00:40.665 --> 00:00:42.083 position:50% align:center line:84%
[MIA]
Awesome!

00:00:42.167 --> 00:00:44.127 position:50% align:center line:84%
What a gorgeous display!

00:00:44.210 --> 00:00:45.962 position:50% align:center line:84%
Our fans just sent them over.

00:00:46.046 --> 00:00:48.715 position:50% align:center line:84%
This is the cutest thing!

00:00:48.798 --> 00:00:51.343 position:50% align:center line:84%
[SHIORIKO]
And they wrote us messages, too!

00:00:51.426 --> 00:00:53.720 position:50% align:center line:84%
That's so nice. I'm tearing up!

00:00:53.803 --> 00:00:55.513 position:50% align:center line:84%
[VICE PRESIDENT A]
Look alive!

00:00:55.597 --> 00:00:58.141 position:50% align:center line:84%
We're about to open the doors!

00:00:58.224 --> 00:01:00.060 position:50% align:center line:84%
Well? Y'ready?

00:01:00.143 --> 00:01:01.853 position:50% align:center line:84%
[GROUP]
Yeah!

00:02:32.444 --> 00:02:37.615 position:50% align:center line:84%
[CROWD chattering]

00:02:37.699 --> 00:02:40.493 position:50% align:center line:84%
Takasaki. Say the word
and we'll get started.

00:02:40.577 --> 00:02:42.704 position:50% align:center line:84%
The stream's ready to go live.

00:02:42.787 --> 00:02:44.456 position:50% align:center line:84%
[YU]
Mm!

00:02:44.539 --> 00:02:45.915 position:50% align:center line:84%
[SETSUNA]
This venue's gigantic,

00:02:45.999 --> 00:02:48.293 position:50% align:center line:84%
and somehow we've
managed to pack it!

00:02:48.376 --> 00:02:51.171 position:50% align:center line:84%
I know. I can't believe that
so many fans showed up,

00:02:51.254 --> 00:02:52.672 position:50% align:center line:84%
and they're here just for us!

00:02:52.756 --> 00:02:55.425 position:50% align:center line:84%
[MIA gasps]

00:02:55.508 --> 00:02:56.634 position:50% align:center line:84%
[KASUMI grumbles]

00:02:56.718 --> 00:02:58.553 position:50% align:center line:84%
Are you getting nervous?

00:02:58.636 --> 00:03:00.638 position:50% align:center line:84%
Do you need me
to hold your hand?

00:03:00.722 --> 00:03:02.349 position:50% align:center line:84%
This is me excited!

00:03:02.432 --> 00:03:04.934 position:50% align:center line:84%
Deep breaths.
How 'bout we circle up?

00:03:05.018 --> 00:03:07.312 position:50% align:center line:84%
Oh, cool! I've never
done this before!

00:03:07.395 --> 00:03:09.647 position:50% align:center line:84%
Then follow our lead.

00:03:09.731 --> 00:03:11.399 position:50% align:center line:84%
How's that feel?

00:03:11.483 --> 00:03:13.610 position:50% align:center line:84%
[RINA]
Good. Thank you.

00:03:13.693 --> 00:03:15.737 position:50% align:center line:84%
Rina Board. Smile.

00:03:15.820 --> 00:03:19.115 position:50% align:center line:84%
Huh? Rinari, are you angry?

00:03:19.199 --> 00:03:20.617 position:50% align:center line:84%
[RINA]
Huh?

00:03:21.743 --> 00:03:23.745 position:50% align:center line:84%
Is it glitching?

00:03:23.828 --> 00:03:26.748 position:50% align:center line:84%
Yep, must be. But no worries.

00:03:26.831 --> 00:03:29.209 position:50% align:center line:84%
I'll figure it out
before my number comes up.

00:03:29.292 --> 00:03:31.753 position:50% align:center line:84%
That is, if you'll help me.

00:03:31.836 --> 00:03:33.296 position:50% align:center line:84%
Of course!

00:03:33.380 --> 00:03:35.715 position:50% align:center line:84%
Enough talk. Let's sing!

00:03:35.799 --> 00:03:38.301 position:50% align:center line:84%
[GROUP]
Yeah!

00:03:38.385 --> 00:03:40.720 position:50% align:center line:84%
[KASUMI] The Nijigasaki
High School Idol Club's

00:03:40.804 --> 00:03:44.391 position:50% align:center line:84%
"First Live with You!"
concert starts now.

00:03:44.474 --> 00:03:46.810 position:50% align:center line:84%
It's the beginning
of a new era for us.

00:03:46.893 --> 00:03:49.729 position:50% align:center line:84%
We're doing this for every
fan who's supported our club

00:03:49.813 --> 00:03:51.690 position:50% align:center line:84%
since we first stepped on stage.

00:03:51.773 --> 00:03:54.693 position:50% align:center line:84%
So we gotta give this our best.
Hold nothing back!

00:03:54.776 --> 00:03:56.528 position:50% align:center line:84%
Together!

00:03:56.611 --> 00:03:59.781 position:50% align:center line:84%
[GROUP] Let's make our
rainbow bloom bright today!

00:04:05.453 --> 00:04:06.830 position:50% align:center line:84%
[CROWD cheering]

00:04:06.913 --> 00:04:09.499 position:50% align:center line:84%
Don't blink. This is the
birth of a new legend.

00:04:09.582 --> 00:04:11.209 position:50% align:center line:84%
Keep us in your hearts!

00:04:26.975 --> 00:04:28.059 position:50% align:center line:84%
They adore her!

00:04:28.143 --> 00:04:30.603 position:50% align:center line:84%
Yes, and you can tell
she's having fun.

00:04:30.687 --> 00:04:33.231 position:50% align:center line:84%
But I'm not gonna let
her outshine me!

00:05:02.052 --> 00:05:04.596 position:50% align:center line:84%
Incoming! Come on now!

00:05:04.679 --> 00:05:07.390 position:50% align:center line:84%
Let's make this the
world's cutest stage.

00:05:07.474 --> 00:05:09.434 position:50% align:center line:84%
Get ready for...

00:05:09.517 --> 00:05:12.645 position:50% align:center line:84%
Giant Kasumin Balloons!

00:05:40.256 --> 00:05:42.509 position:50% align:center line:84%
You're the best Sis!

00:05:45.887 --> 00:05:47.263 position:50% align:center line:84%
[HARUKA laughs]

00:05:56.272 --> 00:05:58.149 position:50% align:center line:84%
Sweet dreams.

00:05:59.150 --> 00:06:01.486 position:50% align:center line:84%
[CROWD screaming]

00:06:01.569 --> 00:06:03.613 position:50% align:center line:84%
[gasps] Ciao!

00:06:19.337 --> 00:06:21.047 position:50% align:center line:84%
It's my sister!

00:06:21.131 --> 00:06:25.844 position:50% align:center line:84%
Smile bright! Let's all
connect our feelings!

00:06:25.927 --> 00:06:27.387 position:50% align:center line:84%
This is not good.

00:06:27.470 --> 00:06:30.432 position:50% align:center line:84%
[AI]
I can't fix it.

00:06:30.515 --> 00:06:32.142 position:50% align:center line:84%
[MIA]
Want me to go on before you?

00:06:32.225 --> 00:06:33.518 position:50% align:center line:84%
[RINA]
Hm?

00:06:33.601 --> 00:06:35.937 position:50% align:center line:84%
[MIA gasping]

00:06:36.021 --> 00:06:39.607 position:50% align:center line:84%
[RINA]
It's okay. I've got this.

00:06:39.691 --> 00:06:41.985 position:50% align:center line:84%
[GIRLS]
Go Rina!

00:06:44.154 --> 00:06:45.488 position:50% align:center line:84%
[ALL gasp]

00:07:03.715 --> 00:07:05.467 position:50% align:center line:84%
[RINA]
Thank you!

00:07:27.489 --> 00:07:31.326 position:50% align:center line:84%
[MIA]
Wow. Rina is amazing.

00:07:31.409 --> 00:07:33.870 position:50% align:center line:84%
And so are the fans.

00:07:33.953 --> 00:07:36.956 position:50% align:center line:84%
Being a school idol...

00:07:37.040 --> 00:07:39.000 position:50% align:center line:84%
...is the best!

00:08:05.276 --> 00:08:07.779 position:50% align:center line:84%
[KARIN] Let's treasure
this moment, everyone.

00:08:09.823 --> 00:08:11.241 position:50% align:center line:84%
That's my cue.

00:08:11.324 --> 00:08:12.867 position:50% align:center line:84%
[RINA]
You'll do great.

00:08:39.769 --> 00:08:42.147 position:50% align:center line:84%
[BOTH]
DiverDiva's in the house!

00:08:42.230 --> 00:08:44.649 position:50% align:center line:84%
Thanks for cheering us on.

00:08:44.733 --> 00:08:46.276 position:50% align:center line:84%
[LANZHU]
Here we go...

00:08:58.580 --> 00:09:00.498 position:50% align:center line:84%
[SETSUNA]
Mia! And Lanzhu?

00:09:00.582 --> 00:09:02.876 position:50% align:center line:84%
Music is better...
when it's shared.

00:09:02.959 --> 00:09:04.377 position:50% align:center line:84%
Are you ready?

00:09:04.461 --> 00:09:06.421 position:50% align:center line:84%
[LANZHU speaking Chinese]

00:09:06.504 --> 00:09:10.550 position:50% align:center line:84%
[CROWD cheers]

00:09:13.428 --> 00:09:14.888 position:50% align:center line:84%
[AI]
Where did that come from?

00:09:14.971 --> 00:09:16.222 position:50% align:center line:84%
It was a surprise.

00:09:16.306 --> 00:09:18.933 position:50% align:center line:84%
[SHIZUKU grumbles]
Let's show them what we've got!

00:09:19.017 --> 00:09:20.143 position:50% align:center line:84%
[AYUMU, SETSUNA]
Yeah!

00:09:54.803 --> 00:09:57.931 position:50% align:center line:84%
We're just getting started,
girls! [laughs]

00:10:10.610 --> 00:10:14.030 position:50% align:center line:84%
Setsuna! You rule!

00:10:47.188 --> 00:10:49.566 position:50% align:center line:84%
Let me hear you, too!

00:10:59.242 --> 00:11:01.369 position:50% align:center line:84%
Ayumu!

00:11:13.089 --> 00:11:15.842 position:50% align:center line:84%
[YU] Can you tell us what
motivates you for the show?

00:11:15.925 --> 00:11:20.305 position:50% align:center line:84%
[AYUMU] Hm. When I first started
off as a school idol,

00:11:20.388 --> 00:11:23.558 position:50% align:center line:84%
it was mostly because I thought
it'd be fun to sing and dance.

00:11:23.641 --> 00:11:26.061 position:50% align:center line:84%
But things have changed.

00:11:26.144 --> 00:11:27.812 position:50% align:center line:84%
I have a bigger goal now.

00:11:27.896 --> 00:11:29.773 position:50% align:center line:84%
I want to pass on
a little happiness

00:11:29.856 --> 00:11:32.192 position:50% align:center line:84%
and courage to the audience!

00:11:32.275 --> 00:11:34.235 position:50% align:center line:84%
[UZUKI] We have ten
minutes of intermission.

00:11:34.319 --> 00:11:36.196 position:50% align:center line:84%
[SATSUKI]
Please change your costumes.

00:11:36.279 --> 00:11:38.615 position:50% align:center line:84%
[EMMA]
Amazing! Come look!

00:11:38.698 --> 00:11:41.868 position:50% align:center line:84%
Our view count's blowing up.
It won't stop.

00:11:41.951 --> 00:11:43.745 position:50% align:center line:84%
[KANATA] There are even
fans from overseas

00:11:43.828 --> 00:11:45.288 position:50% align:center line:84%
tuning in to watch.

00:11:45.372 --> 00:11:49.125 position:50% align:center line:84%
Huh! I wonder if the girl
who sent me that email

00:11:49.209 --> 00:11:50.960 position:50% align:center line:84%
is watching with her friend.

00:11:51.044 --> 00:11:52.253 position:50% align:center line:84%
And there's that.

00:11:52.337 --> 00:11:53.713 position:50% align:center line:84%
Yeah, it must have
been delivered

00:11:53.797 --> 00:11:57.175 position:50% align:center line:84%
after the rest of the flowers.

00:11:57.258 --> 00:11:59.761 position:50% align:center line:84%
Wow, the new members
put on a great show!

00:11:59.844 --> 00:12:01.304 position:50% align:center line:84%
Right?

00:12:04.015 --> 00:12:06.017 position:50% align:center line:84%
[YU]
Look at that crowd.

00:12:06.101 --> 00:12:09.062 position:50% align:center line:84%
Every last one of them is
in love with school idols.

00:12:09.145 --> 00:12:11.523 position:50% align:center line:84%
Aw. It makes me so happy.

00:12:11.606 --> 00:12:12.941 position:50% align:center line:84%
[VICE PRESIDENT A laughs]

00:12:13.024 --> 00:12:14.317 position:50% align:center line:84%
[AYUMU]
Hey, Yu?

00:12:14.401 --> 00:12:15.610 position:50% align:center line:84%
What is it?

00:12:15.694 --> 00:12:17.362 position:50% align:center line:84%
[AYUMU]
We need you backstage.

00:12:20.031 --> 00:12:21.408 position:50% align:center line:84%
[LANZHU]
It's almost time.

00:12:21.491 --> 00:12:23.535 position:50% align:center line:84%
You look quite stunning, Lanzhu.

00:12:23.618 --> 00:12:25.370 position:50% align:center line:84%
[speaking Chinese] Karin.

00:12:25.453 --> 00:12:26.871 position:50% align:center line:84%
Is everything okay?

00:12:26.955 --> 00:12:28.206 position:50% align:center line:84%
There you are.

00:12:28.289 --> 00:12:29.791 position:50% align:center line:84%
Look!

00:12:30.750 --> 00:12:32.252 position:50% align:center line:84%
[YU gasps]

00:12:47.267 --> 00:12:49.519 position:50% align:center line:84%
[gasps]

00:12:49.602 --> 00:12:52.397 position:50% align:center line:84%
I'd expect nothing less
from our thoughtful fans!

00:12:52.480 --> 00:12:53.898 position:50% align:center line:84%
They totally get it.

00:12:53.982 --> 00:12:55.483 position:50% align:center line:84%
[EMMA]
Mm-hm!

00:12:55.567 --> 00:12:59.195 position:50% align:center line:84%
You are far more talented than
I ever expected you would be.

00:12:59.279 --> 00:13:01.156 position:50% align:center line:84%
Wow, thank you.

00:13:01.239 --> 00:13:02.615 position:50% align:center line:84%
Look at us!

00:13:02.699 --> 00:13:05.493 position:50% align:center line:84%
Thirteen must be the School
Idol Club's lucky number.

00:13:05.577 --> 00:13:08.455 position:50% align:center line:84%
[AYUMU] Mm-hm! Because you're
a school idol as well, Yu.

00:13:08.538 --> 00:13:12.208 position:50% align:center line:84%
Huh? No. I just
write songs is all.

00:13:12.292 --> 00:13:13.918 position:50% align:center line:84%
Give yourself more credit.

00:13:14.002 --> 00:13:15.337 position:50% align:center line:84%
Think about it.

00:13:15.420 --> 00:13:17.380 position:50% align:center line:84%
You're able to thrill
not just the audience,

00:13:17.464 --> 00:13:19.299 position:50% align:center line:84%
but the rest of us as well.

00:13:19.382 --> 00:13:20.967 position:50% align:center line:84%
[gasps]

00:13:32.062 --> 00:13:33.855 position:50% align:center line:84%
[UZUKI]
The show starts in two minutes.

00:13:33.938 --> 00:13:34.689 position:50% align:center line:84%
Already?!

00:13:34.773 --> 00:13:36.524 position:50% align:center line:84%
[SHIORIKO]
Let's hurry!

00:13:43.156 --> 00:13:44.741 position:50% align:center line:84%
Jeez...

00:13:45.450 --> 00:13:48.536 position:50% align:center line:84%
[YU] It's not like I can stand
on stage and perform radiantly

00:13:48.620 --> 00:13:51.414 position:50% align:center line:84%
like Ayumu and the others do.

00:13:51.498 --> 00:13:53.667 position:50% align:center line:84%
When I became a club member,

00:13:53.750 --> 00:13:56.169 position:50% align:center line:84%
my main focus was to help
other people discover

00:13:56.252 --> 00:13:58.713 position:50% align:center line:84%
that they love school
idols as much as me.

00:13:58.797 --> 00:14:00.465 position:50% align:center line:84%
Nothing more.

00:14:00.548 --> 00:14:03.593 position:50% align:center line:84%
But this note...

00:14:03.677 --> 00:14:06.429 position:50% align:center line:84%
...hit me hard.

00:14:06.513 --> 00:14:09.974 position:50% align:center line:84%
I'm so touched.
I couldn't be happier.

00:14:10.058 --> 00:14:11.976 position:50% align:center line:84%
Thanks so much!

00:14:17.816 --> 00:14:20.026 position:50% align:center line:84%
[VICE PRESIDENT A] Okay,
intermission is over.

00:14:20.110 --> 00:14:21.027 position:50% align:center line:84%
Last song!

00:14:21.111 --> 00:14:22.737 position:50% align:center line:84%
[GROUP]
Right!

00:14:23.321 --> 00:14:30.203 position:50% align:center line:84%
[CROWD cheering]

00:14:37.168 --> 00:14:39.045 position:50% align:center line:84%
Huh?!

00:14:39.129 --> 00:14:44.801 position:50% align:center line:84%
I love you! Truly!

00:14:44.884 --> 00:14:46.302 position:50% align:center line:84%
[CROWD]
Huh?

00:14:46.386 --> 00:14:47.679 position:50% align:center line:84%
[YU gasps]

00:14:47.762 --> 00:14:51.808 position:50% align:center line:84%
Is that Takasaki?
She's in the club, too.

00:15:00.025 --> 00:15:01.818 position:50% align:center line:84%
You're good.

00:15:08.116 --> 00:15:11.369 position:50% align:center line:84%
[VICE PRESIDENT A] Takasaki,
we're turning on your mic.

00:15:13.705 --> 00:15:15.248 position:50% align:center line:84%
Um. Hi.

00:15:15.331 --> 00:15:17.083 position:50% align:center line:84%
First of all,
thanks for coming to

00:15:17.167 --> 00:15:19.794 position:50% align:center line:84%
the School Idol Club's
first solo concert.

00:15:19.878 --> 00:15:23.965 position:50% align:center line:84%
I'm honestly so happy that it
feels like this isn't even real.

00:15:24.049 --> 00:15:28.595 position:50% align:center line:84%
Ever since I became a member,
I've had the greatest time.

00:15:28.678 --> 00:15:32.515 position:50% align:center line:84%
I wasn't sure that I
deserved so much joy.

00:15:32.599 --> 00:15:34.100 position:50% align:center line:84%
And guess what?

00:15:34.184 --> 00:15:35.810 position:50% align:center line:84%
I don't think I'm
the only person here

00:15:35.894 --> 00:15:37.812 position:50% align:center line:84%
at this Live who feels that way.

00:15:37.896 --> 00:15:39.939 position:50% align:center line:84%
It's the same for you!

00:15:40.023 --> 00:15:43.526 position:50% align:center line:84%
I'm sure all of you have
a dream you're chasing.

00:15:43.610 --> 00:15:45.278 position:50% align:center line:84%
I want you to know
it doesn't matter

00:15:45.362 --> 00:15:48.406 position:50% align:center line:84%
if you have a slow start
or need lots of work.

00:15:48.490 --> 00:15:50.533 position:50% align:center line:84%
And there will be times
when things don't go

00:15:50.617 --> 00:15:54.037 position:50% align:center line:84%
as well as they could.

00:15:54.120 --> 00:15:57.207 position:50% align:center line:84%
But don't worry.
We'll be here for you!

00:15:57.290 --> 00:16:00.919 position:50% align:center line:84%
Whenever you need to smile,
you can call on us!

00:16:01.002 --> 00:16:02.796 position:50% align:center line:84%
[AYUMU]
Take my hand.

00:16:05.340 --> 00:16:06.216 position:50% align:center line:84%
[AYUMU laughs]

00:16:16.309 --> 00:16:19.479 position:50% align:center line:84%
The Nijigasaki School
Idol Club supports you,

00:16:19.562 --> 00:16:22.273 position:50% align:center line:84%
and that is never
going to change.

00:16:22.357 --> 00:16:25.360 position:50% align:center line:84%
[GROUP]
Thank you so much, everyone!

00:16:29.906 --> 00:16:31.408 position:50% align:center line:84%
[KASUMI, KANATA laughing]

00:16:31.491 --> 00:16:37.539 position:50% align:center line:84%
